Package: loco
Title: Model-Free Variable Importance: LOCO
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Kwonsang", "Jung", , "kwons.jung@tamu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An efficient implementation of the Leave-One-Covariate-Out
    (LOCO) framework, a model-free, prediction-based approach to variable
    importance that measures how much predictive accuracy declines when
    each covariate is removed from a fitted model.
